        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 12–24: Pedipalp segments. Figures 12–22. Pandiborellius somalilandus, male from locality No. 19SL, pedipalp chela dorsal (12), external (13) and ventral (14) views, patella dorsal (15), external (16) and ventral (17) views, femur and trochanter dorsal (18), and ventral (19) views, movable finger dentition under white (20) and UV (21) light and fixed finger (22) dentition under UV light. Trichobothrial pattern indicated in Figures 12–18. Figures 23–24. Pandinurus awalei sp. n., male holotype, movable finger (23) and fixed finger (24) dentition under UV light." ;
